    "current_setup": "The runtime now supports up to four PCA9685 boards sharing the Arduino's I2C bus in parallel as one 64-channel global space. The current bench setup uses 61 solenoids across four PCA9685 boards: channels 0 through 60 are wired, with the final board using only its lower 13 channels.",
